                <p xml:lang="heb"><supplied reason="lost">דכ</supplied>רין לטב כל קהלה<lb/>
                    <supplied reason="lost">די</supplied> עבדו הדין פספה<lb/>
                    <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/><orig>ד</orig> אישו ותמה
                    ויהודה <lb/>דיהבו תלתה דינרין <gap reason="illegible" unit="character"
                        quantity="7"/></p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
              
                <p>Remembered for good be the whole community who made this mosaic … Aisu and Thomas
                    and Judah who gave three denarii. [characters]</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>The illegible characters on line four "bear very little resemblance to either
                    Greek or any other script." They may be either "deocrative scrawls" or "magical
                    signs."</p>
            </div>
